org.eclipse.scada.configuration.infrastructure

Interface MasterServer

  • All Superinterfaces:
    EquinoxApplication
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MasterServerImpl

    public interface MasterServer
extends EquinoxApplication
    A representation of the model object 'Master Server'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Authoratives
    • Import Master
    • Driver
    • Archive To
    • Local Credentials

    See Also:
    InfrastructurePackage.getMasterServer()
